        "bullet_point": {
            "value": [
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "NO ASSEMBLY REQUIRED: Ready to use out of the box; Uses wing nut closures for easy set up; No tools required; Run gold paydirt and processed concentrate to maximize your gold recovery efforts",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "COMPACT AND PORTABLE: At only 12” length by 3.5” wide with 1.5\" high channel walls, this aluminum pocket mini sluice box is easy to pack up in your hiking backpack for your next gold prospecting adventure",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "EASY TO USE: Just feed your gold rich paydirt over a moving waterflow through the sluice box channel and watch as the riffles create turbulance in the water depositing the heavy material of fine gold and nuggets within them",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "RUBBER SLUICE BOX MATTING: Includes V-Shape ribbed rubber sluice box matting; Optional woven vinyl miners moss carpet can be installed under the rustproof angled mesh channel inserts if desired",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "LIGHTWEIGHT AND WEATHERPROOF: Constructed from rust resistant aluminum this mini pocket sluice box is durable and built to last; ideal for fine gold recovery from your tailings or concentrate",
